io.github.nucleuspowered.nucleus.api.service

Interface NucleusBlacklistMigrationService

  • Deprecated. 
    The Blacklist has been removed. Will be removed in a future version of Nucleus.

    @Deprecated
public interface NucleusBlacklistMigrationService
    This service provides methods to support obtaining Nucleus' blacklist entries for use by another plugin.
